articles.title: Diet Coke or Coke Zero: Experts give their verdict on which option is healthier - Daily Mail
articles.description: Diet Coke and Coke Zero have zero sugar and are low calorie, but many debate which one is healthier. Dietitians have given DailyMail.com their verdict, along with five other matchups.
articles.content:

articles.title: Genome data sheds light on how Homo sapiens arose in Africa - Reuters
articles.description: Our species arose in Africa more than 300,000 years ago, with the oldest-known Homo sapiens fossils discovered at a site in Morocco called Jebel Irhoud, located between Marrakech and the Atlantic coast.
